msgctxt "sn35.140:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.140:0.2"
msgid "14. Devadahavagga "
msgstr "14. At Devadaha "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 140. Ajjhattaaniccahetusutta → ajjhattaaniccasuttaṃ (bj) | hetunā ajjhatta 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.140:0.3"
msgid "140. Ajjhattaaniccahetusutta "
msgstr "140. Interior and Cause Are Impermanent "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.130, sc1
msgctxt "sn35.140:1.1"
msgid "“Cakkhuṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the eye is impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn35.140:1.2"
msgid "Yopi hetu, yopi paccayo cakkhussa uppādāya, sopi anicco. "
msgstr "The cause and condition that gives rise to the eye is also impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn35.140:1.3"
msgid "Aniccasambhūtaṃ, bhikkhave, cakkhu kuto niccaṃ bhavissati … pe … "
msgstr "Since the eye is produced by what is impermanent, how could it be permanent? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.140:1.4"
msgid "jivhā aniccā. "
msgstr "The ear … nose … tongue … body … "

msgctxt "sn35.140:1.5"
msgid "Yopi hetu, yopi paccayo jivhāya uppādāya sopi anicco. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.140:1.6"
msgid "Aniccasambhūtā, bhikkhave, jivhā kuto niccā bhavissati … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.140:1.7"
msgid "mano anicco. "
msgstr "mind is impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn35.140:1.8"
msgid "Yopi, bhikkhave, hetu yopi paccayo manassa uppādāya, sopi anicco. "
msgstr "The cause and condition that gives rise to the mind is also impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn35.140:1.9"
msgid "Aniccasambhūto, bhikkhave, mano kuto nicco bhavissati. "
msgstr "Since the mind is produced by what is impermanent, how could it be permanent? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.140:1.10"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako cakkhusmimpi nibbindati … pe … jivhāyapi nibbindati … pe … manasmimpi nibbindati, "
msgstr "Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with the eye, ear, nose, tongue, body, and mind. "

msgctxt "sn35.140:1.11"
msgid "nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati; vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.140:1.12"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.140:1.13"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

